name: with-lib
description: This is an example how to include dmocks in your project by using dmocks-revived.lib and dub package manager. Build this using `dub build --build=unittest` inside dir with this file (this will include tests on startup of your app). 'libs' should point to dmocks-revivied.lib, importPaths should point to dmocks-revived source root directory. You should build dmocks before building this project
